Dragon Hunter								KEY:Ranger Archetype ~ Dragon Hunter					CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.RangerArchetype.RangerTrack.RangerFavoredEnemy														PRECLASS:1,Ranger=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Ranger Archetype ~ Dragon Hunter],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.RangerTrack,TYPE.RangerFavoredEnemy]																																																DESC:The quintessential dragonslayers, dragon hunters are experts at forging through the wilds in search of great wyrms.																																																																																																																																																																																																															ABILITY:Ranger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Hunter ~ Class Skills|PRECLASS:1,Ranger=1	ABILITY:Ranger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Hunter ~ Predatory Deduction|PRECLASS:1,Ranger=1	ABILITY:Ranger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Hunter ~ Wyrm Hatred|PRECLASS:1,Ranger=1	ABILITY:Ranger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Hunter ~ Dragoncrafting|PRECLASS:1,Ranger=5	ABILITY:Ranger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Hunter ~ Undaunted|PRECLASS:1,Ranger=10	ABILITY:Ranger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Hunter ~ Expert Dragoncrafter|PRECLASS:1,Ranger=15	ABILITY:Ranger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Hunter ~ Elemental Resilience|PRECLASS:1,Ranger=20																																																																																																																		COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

