Dragon Drinker								KEY:Sorcerer Archetype ~ Dragon Drinker					CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.Sorcerer Archetype.Sorcerer Bloodline.SorcererBloodlineFeats												PRECLASS:1,Sorcerer=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Sorcerer Archetype ~ Dragon Drinker],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.Sorcerer Bloodline,TYPE.SorcererBloodlineFeats]																																														DESC:The blood of dragons not only flows through a dragon drinker's veins, but also empowers her spells and magical abilities when consumed.																																																																																																																																																																																																												ABILITY:Sorcerer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Drinker ~ Bloodline|PRECLASS:1,Sorcerer=1	ABILITY:Sorcerer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Drinker ~ Energy Assimilation|PRECLASS:1,Sorcerer=7	ABILITY:Sorcerer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Drinker ~ Breath Mimicry|PRECLASS:1,Sorcerer=13	ABILITY:Sorcerer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Drinker ~ Blood Siphon|PRECLASS:1,Sorcerer=19																																																																																																																																																																COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

Bloodline									KEY:Dragon Drinker ~ Bloodline						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragon Drinker Class Feature.Sorcerer Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																																																																										DESC:A dragon drinker must belong to the draconic bloodline - At some point in your family's history, a dragon interbred with your bloodline, and now its ancient power flows through your veins.																																																																																																																																																																																																			ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Drinker ~ Bleeding Spells|Draconic Bloodline ~ Bonus Spells	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Drinker ~ Blood Drinking|PREVAREQ:Sorcerer_CF_BloodlinePower1,0	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Draconic Bloodline ~ Dragon Resistances|PREVAREQ:Sorcerer_CF_BloodlinePower3,0|PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Draconic Bloodline ~ Breath Weapon|PREVAREQ:Sorcerer_CF_BloodlinePower9,0|PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Draconic Bloodline ~ Wings|PREVAREQ:Sorcerer_CF_BloodlinePower15,0|PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,15	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Draconic Bloodline ~ Power of Wyrms|PREVAREQ:Sorcerer_CF_BloodlinePower20,0|PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,20									BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Dragon Drinker Draconic Bloodline Choice|1																																																																									CSKILL:Perception					SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Bleeding Spells								KEY:Dragon Drinker ~ Bleeding Spells					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragon Drinker Class Feature.Sorcerer Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																							DESC:Whenever a dragon drinker casts a spell that deals damage, the spell deals 1 point of bleed damage per spell level to any creatures of the dragon type damaged.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Blood Drinking								KEY:Dragon Drinker ~ Blood Drinking						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragon Drinker Class Feature.Sorcerer Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																				DEFINE:DragonBloodHealingDiceNumber|0	DEFINE:DragonBloodAlchemicalBonus|0	DEFINE:DragonBloodHealingDiceSize|0	DESC:A dragon drinker gains the ability to drink a vial of dragon blood as a standard action to alter or augment her spellcasting abilities. A vial of dragon's blood heals %1d%2 points of damage. It also grants a +%3 alchemical bonus on Will and Fortitude saving throws for 1 minute. For the purposes of harvesting dragon's blood, treat the dragon drinker as though she has Dragoncrafting feat.|DragonBloodHealingDiceNumber|DragonBloodHealingDiceSize|DragonBloodAlchemicalBonus	DESC: Drinking a vial of dragon's blood also provides the dragon drinker with a +1 bonus to her caster level for purposes of level-dependent spell effects on a single spell cast within 1 minute.|PREVARGTEQ:SorcererLVL,5	DESC: In the absence of true dragon's blood, the dragon drinker may tap into the draconic blood flowing through her veins to gain the temporary effects of having consumed dragon's blood. As a free action, she can activate this ability, healing ld4 points of damage and gaining a +1 resistance bonus on Will and Fortitude saves for 1 round. This action may only be performed once per round, and can be performed %1 times per day.|3+Sorcerer_Spells_StatBonus																																																																																																																																																																																																			BONUS:VAR|DragonBloodHealingDiceSize|4	BONUS:VAR|DragonBloodHealingDiceSize|4|PREVARGTEQ:SorcererLVL,7	BONUS:VAR|DragonBloodAlchemicalBonus|1	BONUS:VAR|DragonBloodAlchemicalBonus|1|PREVARGTEQ:SorcererLVL,11	BONUS:VAR|DragonBloodHealingDiceNumber|1	BONUS:VAR|DragonBloodHealingDiceNumber|2|PREVARGTEQ:SorcererLVL,19														SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Energy Assimilation							KEY:Dragon Drinker ~ Energy Assimilation					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragon Drinker Class Feature.Sorcerer Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																							DESC:When the dragon drinker drinks true dragon's blood from a dragon with a breath weapon that deals a different type of energy damage than her chosen energy type, she may adopt the energy resistance of the blood's source dragon as if it were her selected bloodline. This effect lasts for 1 minute per dose of dragon's blood, after which the dragon drinker's energy resistance reverts back to her normal energy type.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Breath Mimicry								KEY:Dragon Drinker ~ Breath Mimicry						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragon Drinker Class Feature.Sorcerer Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																							DESC:When the dragon drinker drinks true dragon's blood from a dragon with a breath weapon of a shape or energy type different from her own, she may use the shape and energy type of the blood's source dragon when she next uses her breath weapon.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Blood Siphon								KEY:Dragon Drinker ~ Blood Siphon						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragon Drinker Class Feature.Sorcerer Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																							DESC:When the dragon drinker is within 60 feet of a creature of the dragon type that is suffering bleed damage, she can, as a swift action, draw a dose of its blood into herself as though she had consumed it from a vial.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.22

